      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0365P0_20010321_WH_41'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-eric-illsley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0365P0_20010321_WH_41' title='Link to this speech by Mr Eric Illsley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-eric-illsley" title="Mr Eric Illsley">Mr. Eric Illsley (in the Chair)</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Before I call the hon. Member for Taunton (Jackie Ballard), may I ask the three party spokespersons to respect the convention of speaking for only 10 minutes each?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
